 821 @{i}Simple Mail Transfer Protocol@{ui}, by Jonathon B. Postel, August 1982.
 822 @{i}Standard for the Format of ARPA Internet Text Messages@{ui}, revised by David H. Crocker, August 1982.
1321 @{i}The MD5 Message-Digest Algorithm@{ui}, by R. Rivest, April 1992.
1344 @{i}Implications of MIME for Internet Mail Gateways@{ui}, by N. Borenstein, June 1992.
1524 @{i}A User Agent Configuration Mechanism for Multimedia Mail Format Identification@{ui}, by N. Borenstein, September 1993.
1896 @{i}The text/enriched MIME content type@{ui}, by P. Resnick, A. Walker, February 1996.
1939 @{i}Post Office Protocol - Version 3@{ui}, by J. Myers, M. Rose, May 1996.
2015 @{i}MIME Security with Pretty Good Privacy (PGP)@{ui}, by M. Elkins, October 1996.
2045 @{i}Multipurpose Internet Mail Extensions (MIME) Part One: Format of Internet Message Bodies@{ui}, by N. Freed, N. Borenstein, November 1996.
2046 @{i}Multipurpose Internet Mail Extensions (MIME) Part Two: Media Types@{ui}, by N. Freed, N. Borenstein, November 1996.
2047 @{i}Multipurpose Internet Mail Extensions (MIME) Part Three: Message Header Extensions for Non-ASCII Text@{ui}, by K. Moore, November 1996.
2048 @{i}Multipurpose Internet Mail Extensions (MIME) Part Four: Registration Procedures@{ui}, by N. Freed, J. Klensin, J. Postel, November 1996.
2049 @{i}Multipurpose Internet Mail Extensions (MIME) Part Five: Conformance Criteria and Examples@{ui}, by N. Freed, N. Borenstein, November 1996.
2076 @{i}Common Internet Message Headers@{ui}, by J. Palme, February 1997.

